channel.title: Trading Problem with my RSPS. IMPORTANT
channel.description:

Someone please help! Any help is appreciated, even if you think it's wrong.!

			}
		Client ot = (Client) Server.playerHandler.players[c.tradeWith];
		if(ot == null) {
			c.getTradeAndDuel().declineTrade();
			c.sendMessage("Trade declined as the other player has disconnected.");
